In the Matter of KEDSON’S SPORT SHOP, Inc., Bankrupt. Irving Trust Company, as Trustee in Bankruptcy of Kedson’s Sport Shop, Inc., Appellee, Minnie Kedson, Appellant. No. 265. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Feb. 13, 1934. Shaine & Weinrib, of Now York City (Benjamin Seligman and Maurice L. Shaine, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Gustave J. Rosen, of New York City, for appellee.

Before MANTON, L. HAND, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed.
